Nope, it's something carriable. Okay, I'll just tell you right now, since I already know from raocow's video. This is actually a P-switch, and you'll need it a little further on.

Okay, this is a bit tricky. First of all, that's a real mushroom that was on the turn blocks. Secondly, the center three turn blocks are breakable, and you'll need to break at least one. Now, you're given three Mushells from these ? blocks, and you need to hit the leftmost turn block to reveal a vine (the right block has one coin).
